channel.title: I can't run MoparScape
channel.description:
Yesterday, I was playing away on private servers.. and today all of a sudden, no matter what I do, I get a little red X at top left of my MoparScape webclient.
I tried re-installing Java, removing all cookies, temp. internet files, and history. Nothing.
I'll try some more stuff, but until then, please post, maybe give me some advice..?
